11
00:00:59,775 --> 00:01:02,880
As you\hlisten, think about two questions.

12
00:01:04,320 --> 00:01:14,320
One: what language is used to make suggestions?
Two: what language is used to accept suggestions?\h

13
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:18,960
Ready? Let’s listen to the dialogue.

14
00:01:20,160 --> 00:01:23,920
It’s a lovely day. Why don’t we go out somewhere?
