accept and reject suggestions politely in English.

81
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:32,320
Are we done? Not yet! There’s\h
one more important point.

82
00:07:36,066 --> 00:07:39,040
When you’re accepting a suggestion,

83
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:43,760
intonation is critical. Even if\h
you use correct, polite language,\h\h

84
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:47,680
